ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectOrder Repealing Order in Council P.C. 2008-12 and Designating the Minister of Health as the appropriate Minister with respect to the Canadian Food Inspection Agency for the purposes of the Act
PrecisOrder (1) repealing P.C. 2008-12 of January 16, 2008; and (2) designating the Minister of Health as the appropriate Minister with respect to the Canadian Food Inspection Agency for the purposes of the Financial Administration Act, effective October 7, 2013.
